{"tha-ap2:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap2:0.2":"Buddhavagga ","tha-ap2:0.3":"Paccekabuddhaapadana ","tha-ap2:1.1":"Atha paccekabuddhapadanam sunatha—","tha-ap2:2.1":"“Tathagatam jetavane vasantam, ","tha-ap2:2.2":"Apucchi vedehamuni natango; ","tha-ap2:2.3":"‘Paccekabuddha kira nama honti, ","tha-ap2:2.4":"Bhavanti te hetubhi kehi vira’. ","tha-ap2:3.1":"Tadaha sabbannuvaro mahesi, ","tha-ap2:3.2":"Anandabhaddam madhurassarena; ","tha-ap2:3.3":"‘Ye pubbabuddhesu katadhikara, ","tha-ap2:3.4":"Aladdhamokkha jinasasanesu. ","tha-ap2:4.1":"Teneva samvegamukhena dhira, ","tha-ap2:4.2":"Vinapi buddhehi sutikkhapanna; ","tha-ap2:4.3":"Arammanenapi parittakena, ","tha-ap2:4.4":"Paccekabodhim anupapunanti. ","tha-ap2:5.1":"Sabbamhi lokamhi mamam thapetva, ","tha-ap2:5.2":"Paccekabuddhehi samova natthi; ","tha-ap2:5.3":"Tesam imam vannapadesamattam, ","tha-ap2:5.4":"Vakkhamaham sadhu mahamuninam. ","tha-ap2:6.1":"Sayameva buddhanam mahaisinam, ","tha-ap2:6.2":"Sadhuni vakyani madhuva khuddam; ","tha-ap2:6.3":"Anuttaram bhesajam patthayanta, ","tha-ap2:6.4":"Sunatha sabbesu pasannacitta’. ","tha-ap2:7.1":"Paccekabuddhanam samagatanam, ","tha-ap2:7.2":"Paramparam byakaranani yani; ","tha-ap2:7.3":"Adinavo yanca viragavatthum, ","tha-ap2:7.4":"Yatha ca bodhim anupapunimsu. ","tha-ap2:8.1":"Saragavatthusu viragasanni, ","tha-ap2:8.2":"Rattamhi lokamhi virattacitta; ","tha-ap2:8.3":"Hitva papance jiya phanditani, ","tha-ap2:8.4":"Tatheva bodhim anupapunimsu. ","tha-ap2:9.1":"Sabbesu bhutesu nidhaya dandam, ","tha-ap2:9.2":"Avihethayam annatarampi tesam; ","tha-ap2:9.3":"Mettena cittena hitanukampi, ","tha-ap2:9.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo. ","tha-ap2:10.1":"Sabbesu bhutesu nidhaya dandam, ","tha-ap2:10.2":"Avihethayam annatarampi tesam; ","tha-ap2:10.3":"Na puttamiccheyya kuto sahayam, ","tha-ap2:10.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:11.1":"‘Samsaggajatassa bhavanti sneha, ","tha-ap2:11.2":"Snehanvayam dukkhamidam pahoti; ","tha-ap2:11.3":"Adinavam snehajam pekkhamano, ","tha-ap2:11.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:12.1":"‘Mitte suhajje anukampamano, ","tha-ap2:12.2":"Hapeti attham patibaddhacitto; ","tha-ap2:12.3":"Etam bhayam santhave pekkhamano, ","tha-ap2:12.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:13.1":"‘Vamso visalova yatha visatto, ","tha-ap2:13.2":"Puttesu daresu ca ya apekkha; ","tha-ap2:13.3":"Vamse kalirova asajjamano, ","tha-ap2:13.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:14.1":"‘Migo arannamhi yatha abaddho, ","tha-ap2:14.2":"Yenicchakam gacchati gocaraya; ","tha-ap2:14.3":"Vinnu naro seritam pekkhamano, ","tha-ap2:14.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:15.1":"‘Amantana hoti sahayamajjhe, ","tha-ap2:15.2":"Vase ca thane gamane carikaya; ","tha-ap2:15.3":"Anabhijjhitam seritam pekkhamano, ","tha-ap2:15.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:16.1":"‘Khidda rati hoti sahayamajjhe, ","tha-ap2:16.2":"Puttesu pemam vipulanca hoti; ","tha-ap2:16.3":"Piyavippayogam vijigucchamano, ","tha-ap2:16.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:17.1":"‘Catuddiso appatigho ca hoti, ","tha-ap2:17.2":"Santussamano itaritarena; ","tha-ap2:17.3":"Parissayanam sahita achambhi, ","tha-ap2:17.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:18.1":"‘Dussangaha pabbajitapi eke, ","tha-ap2:18.2":"Atho gahattha gharamavasanta; ","tha-ap2:18.3":"Appossukko paraputtesu hutva, ","tha-ap2:18.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:19.1":"‘Oropayitva gihibyanjanani, ","tha-ap2:19.2":"Sanchinnapatto yatha kovilaro; ","tha-ap2:19.3":"Chetvana viro gihibandhanani, ","tha-ap2:19.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:20.1":"‘Sace labhetha nipakam sahayam, ","tha-ap2:20.2":"Saddhim caram sadhuviharidhiram; ","tha-ap2:20.3":"Abhibhuyya sabbani parissayani, ","tha-ap2:20.4":"Careyya tenattamano satima’. ","tha-ap2:21.1":"‘No ce labhetha nipakam sahayam, ","tha-ap2:21.2":"Saddhim caram sadhuvihari dhiram; ","tha-ap2:21.3":"Rajava rattham vijitam pahaya, ","tha-ap2:21.4":"Eko care matangaranneva nago’. ","tha-ap2:22.1":"‘Addha pasamsama sahayasampadam, ","tha-ap2:22.2":"Settha sama sevitabba sahaya; ","tha-ap2:22.3":"Ete aladdha anavajjabhoji, ","tha-ap2:22.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:23.1":"‘Disva suvannassa pabhassarani, ","tha-ap2:23.2":"Kammaraputtena sunitthitani; ","tha-ap2:23.3":"Sanghattamanani duve bhujasmim, ","tha-ap2:23.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:24.1":"‘Evam dutiyena saha mamassa, ","tha-ap2:24.2":"Vacabhilapo abhisajjana va; ","tha-ap2:24.3":"Etam bhayam ayatim pekkhamano, ","tha-ap2:24.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:25.1":"‘Kama hi citra madhura manorama, ","tha-ap2:25.2":"Viruparupena mathenti cittam; ","tha-ap2:25.3":"Adinavam kamagunesu disva, ","tha-ap2:25.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:26.1":"‘Iti ca gando ca upaddavo ca, ","tha-ap2:26.2":"Rogo ca sallanca bhayanca metam; ","tha-ap2:26.3":"Etam bhayam kamagunesu disva, ","tha-ap2:26.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:27.1":"‘Sitanca unhanca khudam pipasam, ","tha-ap2:27.2":"Vatatape damsasarisape ca; ","tha-ap2:27.3":"Sabbanipetani abhibbhavitva, ","tha-ap2:27.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:28.1":"‘Nagova yuthani vivajjayitva, ","tha-ap2:28.2":"Sanjatakhandho padumi ularo; ","tha-ap2:28.3":"Yathabhirantam viharam aranne, ","tha-ap2:28.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:29.1":"‘Atthana tam sanganikaratassa, ","tha-ap2:29.2":"Yam phassaye samayikam vimuttim; ","tha-ap2:29.3":"Adiccabandhussa vaco nisamma, ","tha-ap2:29.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:30.1":"‘Ditthivisukani upativatto, ","tha-ap2:30.2":"Patto niyamam patiladdhamaggo; ","tha-ap2:30.3":"Uppannananomhi anannaneyyo, ","tha-ap2:30.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:31.1":"‘Nillolupo nikkuho nippipaso, ","tha-ap2:31.2":"Nimmakkha niddhantakasavamoho; ","tha-ap2:31.3":"Nirasayo sabbaloke bhavitva, ","tha-ap2:31.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:32.1":"‘Papam sahayam parivajjayetha, ","tha-ap2:32.2":"Anatthadassim visame nivittham; ","tha-ap2:32.3":"Sayam na seve pasutam pamattam, ","tha-ap2:32.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:33.1":"‘Bahussutam dhammadharam bhajetha, ","tha-ap2:33.2":"Mittam ularam patibhanavantam; ","tha-ap2:33.3":"Annaya atthani vineyya kankham, ","tha-ap2:33.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:34.1":"‘Khiddam ratim kamasukhanca loke, ","tha-ap2:34.2":"Analankaritva anapekkhamano; ","tha-ap2:34.3":"Vibhusatthana virato saccavadi, ","tha-ap2:34.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:35.1":"‘Puttanca daram pitaranca mataram, ","tha-ap2:35.2":"Dhanani dhannani ca bandhavani; ","tha-ap2:35.3":"Hitvana kamani yathodhikani, ","tha-ap2:35.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:36.1":"‘Sango eso parittamettha sokhyam, ","tha-ap2:36.2":"Appassado dukkhamevettha bhiyyo; ","tha-ap2:36.3":"Galo eso iti natva matima, ","tha-ap2:36.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:37.1":"‘Sandalayitvana samyojanani, ","tha-ap2:37.2":"Jalamva bhetva salilambucari; ","tha-ap2:37.3":"Aggiva daddham anivattamano, ","tha-ap2:37.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:38.1":"‘Okkhittacakkhu na ca padalolo, ","tha-ap2:38.2":"Guttindriyo rakkhitamanasano; ","tha-ap2:38.3":"Anavassuto aparidayhamano, ","tha-ap2:38.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:39.1":"‘Oharayitva gihibyanjanani, ","tha-ap2:39.2":"Sanchannapatto yatha parichatto; ","tha-ap2:39.3":"Kasayavattho abhinikkhamitva, ","tha-ap2:39.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:40.1":"‘Rasesu gedham akaram alolo, ","tha-ap2:40.2":"Anannaposi sapadanacari; ","tha-ap2:40.3":"Kule kule appatibaddhacitto, ","tha-ap2:40.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:41.1":"‘Pahaya pancavaranani cetaso, ","tha-ap2:41.2":"Upakkilese byapanujja sabbe; ","tha-ap2:41.3":"Anissito chejja sinehadosam, ","tha-ap2:41.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:42.1":"‘Vipitthikatvana sukhanca dukkham, ","tha-ap2:42.2":"Pubbeva somanassadomanassam; ","tha-ap2:42.3":"Laddhanupekkham samatham visuddham, ","tha-ap2:42.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:43.1":"‘Araddhaviriyo paramatthapattiya, ","tha-ap2:43.2":"Alinacitto akusitavutti; ","tha-ap2:43.3":"Dalhanikkamo thamabalupapanno, ","tha-ap2:43.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:44.1":"‘Patisallanam jhanamarincamano, ","tha-ap2:44.2":"Dhammesu niccam anudhammacari; ","tha-ap2:44.3":"Adinavam sammasita bhavesu, ","tha-ap2:44.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:45.1":"‘Tanhakkhayam patthayamappamatto, ","tha-ap2:45.2":"Anelamugo sutava satima; ","tha-ap2:45.3":"Sankhatadhammo niyato padhanava, ","tha-ap2:45.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:46.1":"‘Sihova saddesu asantasanto, ","tha-ap2:46.2":"Vatova jalamhi asajjamano; ","tha-ap2:46.3":"Padumamva toyena alippamano, ","tha-ap2:46.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:47.1":"‘Siho yatha dathabali pasayha, ","tha-ap2:47.2":"Raja miganam abhibhuyya cari; ","tha-ap2:47.3":"Sevetha pantani senasanani, ","tha-ap2:47.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:48.1":"‘Mettam upekkham karunam vimuttim, ","tha-ap2:48.2":"Asevamano muditanca kale; ","tha-ap2:48.3":"Sabbena lokena avirujjhamano, ","tha-ap2:48.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:49.1":"‘Raganca dosanca pahaya moham, ","tha-ap2:49.2":"Sandalayitvana samyojanani; ","tha-ap2:49.3":"Asantasam jivitasankhayamhi, ","tha-ap2:49.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:50.1":"‘Bhajanti sevanti ca karanattha, ","tha-ap2:50.2":"Nikkarana dullabha ajja mitta; ","tha-ap2:50.3":"Attatthapanna asucimanussa, ","tha-ap2:50.4":"Eko care khaggavisanakappo’. ","tha-ap2:51.1":"Visuddhasila suvisuddhapanna, ","tha-ap2:51.2":"Samahita jagariyanuyutta; ","tha-ap2:51.3":"Vipassaka dhammavisesadassi, ","tha-ap2:51.4":"Maggangabojjhangagate vijanna. ","tha-ap2:52.1":"Sunnappanidhinca tathanimittam, ","tha-ap2:52.2":"Asevayitva jinasasanamhi; ","tha-ap2:52.3":"Ye savakattam na vajanti dhira, ","tha-ap2:52.4":"Bhavanti paccekajina sayambhu. ","tha-ap2:53.1":"Mahantadhamma bahudhammakaya, ","tha-ap2:53.2":"Cittissara sabbadukkhoghatinna; ","tha-ap2:53.3":"Udaggacitta paramatthadassi, ","tha-ap2:53.4":"Sihopama khaggavisanakappa. ","tha-ap2:54.1":"Santindriya santamana samadhi, ","tha-ap2:54.2":"Paccantasattesu patippacara; ","tha-ap2:54.3":"Dipa parattha idha vijjalanta, ","tha-ap2:54.4":"Paccekabuddha satatam hitame. ","tha-ap2:55.1":"Pahinasabbavarana janinda, ","tha-ap2:55.2":"Lokappadipa ghanakancanabha; ","tha-ap2:55.3":"Nissamsayam lokasudakkhineyya, ","tha-ap2:55.4":"Paccekabuddha satatappitame. ","tha-ap2:56.1":"Paccekabuddhanam subhasitani, ","tha-ap2:56.2":"Caranti lokamhi sadevakamhi; ","tha-ap2:56.3":"Sutva tatha ye na karonti bala, ","tha-ap2:56.4":"Caranti dukkhesu punappunam te. ","tha-ap2:57.1":"Paccekabuddhana subhasitani, ","tha-ap2:57.2":"Madhum yatha khuddamavassavantam; ","tha-ap2:57.3":"Sutva tatha ye patipattiyutta, ","tha-ap2:57.4":"Bhavanti te saccadasa sapanna. ","tha-ap2:58.1":"Paccekabuddhehi jinehi bhasita, ","tha-ap2:58.2":"Katha ulara abhinikkhamitva; ","tha-ap2:58.3":"Ta sakyasihena naruttamena, ","tha-ap2:58.4":"Pakasita dhammavijananattham. ","tha-ap2:59.1":"Lokanukampaya imani tesam, ","tha-ap2:59.2":"Paccekabuddhana vikubbitani; ","tha-ap2:59.3":"Samvegasangamativaddhanattham, ","tha-ap2:59.4":"Sayambhusihena pakasitani”ti. ","tha-ap2:60.1":"Paccekabuddhapadanam samattam. "}